一下就收起来，不用来回切窗口了。常驻菜单栏，不占 Dock 位置，强迫症友好。<br /><br />开源免费，有相同需求的朋友可以试试。 <br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/pfPhFye.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pfPhFye.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a><br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/QTcxb8Y.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QTcxb8Y.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a><br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/alexcding/gemini-desktop-mac/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://github.com/alexcding/gemini-desktop-mac/</a>", "last_modified": 1765659507, "replies": 31, "id": 1178747}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4f2/3670/260_large.png?m=1650095354", "name": "security", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4f2/3670/260_normal.png?m=1650095354", "title": "信息安全", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/security", "topics": 1949, "footer": "", "header": "我们都希望自己管理的计算机系统在运转过程中不要遇到任何安全事件。只是，这个不完美的世界的现实告诉我们：学无止境。", "title_alternative": "Security", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4f2/3670/260_mini.png?m=1650095354", "stars": 2092, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 260, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 153377, "username": "Duolingo", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Duolingo", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1c43/7e17/153377_mini.png?m=1765694477", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1c43/7e17/153377_normal.png?m=1765694477", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1c43/7e17/153377_large.png?m=1765694477", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1c43/7e17/153377_xlarge.png?m=1765694477", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1c43/7e17/153377_xxlarge.png?m=1765694477", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1c43/7e17/153377_xxxlarge.png?m=1765694477", "created": 1451365155, "last_modified": 1765694477, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "huage", "last_touched": 1765727691, "title": "火绒阻止了两个奇怪的请求。clash 跑路后，新版内核是否存在问题？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1178803", "created": 1765695393, "deleted": 0, "content": "**电脑空载**的情况下（只挂着 clash verge ），**火绒**突然弹出了拦截窗口，网络防护自动拦截了两次访问请求。\r\n\r\n在安全日志中，都显示为**恶意网址拦截**：\r\n\r\n> `svchost.exe （ msedge.exe ）` 尝试访问 ` [ file.uhsea.com ] `，已阻止。\r\n\r\n搜索相关文档，发现相关讨论（ linuxdo 也有类似讨论）：\r\n<https://github.com/2dust/v2rayN/discussions/7670>\r\n\r\n疑似以下软件都有出现这个问题\r\n* **Clash Verge Singbox V2rayN**\r\n\r\n结合都是用的 **mihomo** 的内核，所以是否可以合理怀疑存在**后门**，或某种可以通过配置文件控制的**漏洞**？\r\n\r\nuhsea 被火绒划为钓鱼仿冒，想不通在后台自动访问的目的。", "content_rendered": "<p><strong>电脑空载</strong>的情况下（只挂着 clash verge ），<strong>火绒</strong>突然弹出了拦截窗口，网络防护自动拦截了两次访问请求。</p>\n<p>在安全日志中，都显示为<strong>恶意网址拦截</strong>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code>svchost.exe （ msedge.exe ）</code> 尝试访问 <code>[ <a href=\"http://file.uhsea.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">file.uhsea.com</a> ]</code>，已阻止。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>搜索相关文档，发现相关讨论（ linuxdo 也有类似讨论）：\n<a href=\"https://github.com/2dust/v2rayN/discussions/7670\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/2dust/v2rayN/discussions/7670</a></p>\n<p>疑似以下软件都有出现这个问题</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Clash Verge Singbox V2rayN</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p>结合都是用的 <strong>mihomo</strong> 的内核，所以是否可以合理怀疑存在<strong>后门</strong>，或某种可以通过配置文件控制的<strong>漏洞</strong>？</p>\n<p>uhsea 被火绒划为钓鱼仿冒，想不通在后台自动访问的目的。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1765709531, "replies": 31, "id": 1178803}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1751718333", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1751718333", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 235753, "footer": "", "header": "<!--\r\n一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。\r\n-->", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1751718333", "stars": 4435, "aliases"